<h1>砧</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">zhēn</span><span class=alesi>(zhen1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 砧 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 砧</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/anvil" style="color:black;">anvil</a>; <a href="/dictionary/flat" style="color:black;">flat</a> <a href="/dictionary/stone" style="color:black;">stone</a>; exe</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 10<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 10 strokes: <a href="/character/能" title="neng2: to be able; can, permitted to; ability">能</a>, <a href="/character/家" title="jia1: house, home, residence; family">家</a>, <a href="/character/都" title="dou1: metropolis, capital; all, the whole; elegant, refined">都</a>, <a href="/character/起" title="qi3: rise, stand up; go up; begin">起</a>, <a href="/character/部" title="bu4: part, division, section">部</a>, <a href="/character/样" title="yang4: shape, form, pattern, style">样</a>, <a href="/character/高" title="gao1: high, tall; lofty, elevated">高</a>, <a href="/character/被" title="">被</a>, <a href="/character/特" title="te4: special, unique, distinguished">特</a>, <a href="/character/海" title="hai3: sea, ocean; maritime">海</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/石" title="Kangxi radical 112">石</a>&nbsp;112.5</p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 4371</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 4476</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/砧木" title="zhen1 mu4">砧木</a>, <a href="/dictionary/砧板" title="zhen1 ban3">砧板</a>, <a href="/dictionary/砧骨" title="zhen1 gu3">砧骨</a>, <a href="/dictionary/角砧" title="jiao3 zhen1">角砧</a>, <a href="/dictionary/铁砧" title="tie3 zhen1">铁砧</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">砧[<span style="color:#990000;">zhēn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- anvil<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">碪|砧[